{"tid":1937614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地網劇需完整劇本送審","createTime":"2020-03-22T04:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T04:54:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"06633b82d86bade6c4b2855902ed2ab33b0e82a1","tid":1937614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T04:54:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200322/GOHNK7VYGHJUPNGKK2AHNH7Y4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200322%2FGOHNK7VYGHJUPNGKK2AHNH7Y4I%2F&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=2232a75f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200322%2FGOHNK7VYGHJUPNGKK2AHNH7Y4I%2F&h=9574d3a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200322/GOHNK7VYGHJUPNGKK2AHNH7Y4I/</a><br />\n<br />\n內地網劇需完整劇本送審<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200322/large/1584797000_2a81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200322%2Flarge%2F1584797000_2a81.jpg&h=e9a56037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地審查制度越來越嚴重，管虎的《八佰》至今仍禁映。劇照<br />\n<br />\n內地廣電局為加強對網絡作品審核，近日又有新規例，要求製作單位要把完整劇本送去審批，跟一向以往只拿大綱送審的模式完全不同。各省局每月將對申報作品進行劇本審核，沒問題才再送去廣電總局，獲批後才發批文開拍。武肺疫情已令內地影視製作一度全部停止，最近才僅有約一成復工，加上戲院經營困難，影視業一池死水，如今廣電總局還要來一個新規例，絕對是雪上加霜。<br />\n<br />\n新規例下，製作公司要先將幾十集劇本寫好送審，要先支付一般30集劇本約400至500萬人民幣的編劇費，如果劇本送審失敗，影視網站就不會買版權，劇本費便由製作公司承擔。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：鍾國仁"}]}